1
00:00:01,500 --> 00:00:06,520
字幕制作：大賬簿

2
00:00:33,930 --> 00:00:37,242
我叫阿希，是個奴隸
<i>My name is Ash. And I am a slave.</i>

3
00:00:40,765 --> 00:00:43,746
照我的判斷，現在是西元1300年...
<i>Close as I can figure it,</i>
<i>the year is 1300 AD...</i>

4
00:00:43,813 --> 00:00:46,314
...我被拖曳著踏上死亡路程
<i>... and I am being dragged to my death.</i>

5
00:00:46,493 --> 00:00:48,331
事情一開始不是這樣的
<i>It wasn't always like this.</i>

6
00:00:49,442 --> 00:00:51,383
我也有過真實的生活
<i>I had a real life once.</i>

7
00:00:53,328 --> 00:00:54,492
還有一份工作
<i>A job.</i>

8
00:01:01,034 --> 00:01:04,780
五金，12號走道
來美而廉，保證物美價廉
Hardware. Aisle 12.
Shop smart, shop S. Mart.

9
00:01:05,355 --> 00:01:08,359
我有個很好的女朋友，玲達
<i>I had a wonderful girlfriend, Linda.</i>

10
00:01:11,586 --> 00:01:14,898
我們一起開車到山上小屋渡假
<i>Together we drove to a small cabin</i>
<i>in the mountains.</i>

11
00:01:18,957 --> 00:01:21,938
有位考古學家來到這偏僻的地方...
<i>It seems an archeologist</i>
<i>had come to this remote place...</i>

12
00:01:22,006 --> 00:01:24,610
...致力翻譯與研究他的最新發現
<i>... to translate and study his latest find.</i>

13
00:01:25,690 --> 00:01:30,168
死亡志記
<i>Necronomicon ex Mortis.</i>
<i>The Book of the Dead.</i>

14
00:01:32,559 --> 00:01:35,837
書本用人皮制成，以血液書寫...
<i>Bound in human flesh and inked in blood...</i>

15
00:01:36,076 --> 00:01:40,325
...這古籍記載了玄奇的埋葬儀式...
<i>... this ancient Sumerian text contained</i>
<i>bizarre burial rites...</i>

16
00:01:40,700 --> 00:01:45,212
...咒語以及惡魔複活等文字
<i>... funerary incantations</i>
<i>and demon resurrection passages.</i>

17
00:01:46,596 --> 00:01:49,302
此書根本就不應存在人間
<i>It was never meant</i>
<i>for the world of the living.</i>

18
00:01:49,779 --> 00:01:52,623
它喚醒了樹林中的邪魔
<i>The book awoke something</i>
<i>dark in the woods.</i>

19
00:01:59,561 --> 00:02:00,999
玲達被抓走了
<i>It took Linda.</i>

20
00:02:02,175 --> 00:02:04,150
然後又來抓我
<i>And then it came for me.</i>

21
00:02:05,625 --> 00:02:10,605
邪魔進到我手
我只好斷腕自保
<i>It got into my hand and it went bad.</i>
<i>So I lopped it off at the wrist.</i>

22
00:02:16,882 --> 00:02:19,520
但它沒完沒了，又回來找我
<i>But that didn't stop it. It came back.</i>

23
00:02:22,276 --> 00:02:23,543
弄得天翻地覆
<i>Big time.</i>

24
00:02:40,969 --> 00:02:44,315
天啊！怎麼讓它停止？
For God's sake! How do you stop it?

25
00:03:06,230 --> 00:03:10,239
魔界英豪

26
00:03:41,273 --> 00:03:43,145
堵住他！
Surround the stranger!

27
00:03:56,181 --> 00:03:58,956
我這是...
Where the hell...

28
00:04:10,956 --> 00:04:14,096
別沖動，老大
我不知道怎麼來到這堛
Easy now, chief.
I don't know how I got here.

29
00:04:14,742 --> 00:04:18,557
我也不想找麻煩
And I'm not looking for any trouble.

30
00:04:21,677 --> 00:04:23,413
這胄甲真堅固！
What a piece of armor this is!

31
00:04:25,094 --> 00:04:26,190
智者！
Wiseman!

32
00:04:31,928 --> 00:04:35,639
陛下，他一定就是志記奡ㄗ鴘漕洈
My lord, I believe he is the one
written of in the Necronomicon.

33
00:04:36,116 --> 00:04:38,525
預言說到他將從天而降...
He who is prophesied to fall
from the heavens...

34
00:04:38,595 --> 00:04:41,073
...挽救我們於鬼怪之手
...and deliver us from
the terrors of the Deadites.

35
00:04:41,342 --> 00:04:43,078
什麼？那個傻子？
What? That buffoon?

36
00:04:43,419 --> 00:04:44,686
他...
Likely...

37
00:04:45,095 --> 00:04:47,504
...比較像亨利手下的人
...he's one of Henry's men!

38
00:04:48,679 --> 00:04:51,214
跪下，混球！
Kneel, rapscallion!

39
00:04:52,532 --> 00:04:54,701
我說，把他丟進深坑堙I
I say, to the pit with him!

40
00:04:59,098 --> 00:05:02,307
-進坑！
-你這可憐的混球
. To the pit!
. You miserable bastard!

41
00:05:04,224 --> 00:05:05,720
別抓我
Get off of me!

42
00:05:08,144 --> 00:05:09,480
放開我！
Let me go!

43
00:05:18,061 --> 00:05:19,557
進城堡！
To the castle!

44
00:05:23,152 --> 00:05:26,624
抬起腳！別拖著！快！
Pick up your feet!
Stop dragging your feet! Come on!

45
00:05:26,804 --> 00:05:31,590
走，快點，快，快點
Move along. Come on, now.
Come on, pick it up.

46
00:05:32,500 --> 00:05:34,533
嘗嘗這個的厲害
Have a taste of this!

47
00:05:41,411 --> 00:05:42,575
好了！
All right, you men!

48
00:05:42,684 --> 00:05:46,933
回到城堡後你將有個驚喜
You've got something to look forward to
when you get back to the castle!

49
00:05:47,676 --> 00:05:51,319
亞瑟王來到！開鐵門！
Lord Arthur approaches!
Raise the portcullis!

50
00:05:53,371 --> 00:05:57,288
亞瑟王！亞瑟王來到！
Lord Arthur! Lord Arthur approaches!

51
00:06:47,477 --> 00:06:51,692
亞瑟王，我兄弟呢？沒跟您一起嗎？
Lord Arthur, where is my brother?
Did he not ride with you?

52
00:06:51,899 --> 00:06:53,898
啊，驍勇善戰
Aye, and fought valiantly.

53
00:06:54,579 --> 00:06:57,617
但昨晚他在與亨利公爵一戰中捐軀了
But last night he fell in battle
to Duke Henry's men.

54
00:06:58,432 --> 00:06:59,870
很抱歉，席拉
I'm sorry, Sheila.

55
00:07:01,112 --> 00:07:03,111
-來
-你這白癡！
. Come on.
. You cretin!

56
00:07:04,161 --> 00:07:05,691
住手，雜種！
Stop it, you bastards!

57
00:07:07,243 --> 00:07:08,681
野蠻人！
Barbarians!

58
00:07:11,196 --> 00:07:13,731
住手！住手，你這雜種！
Stop it! Stop it, you little bastards!

59
00:07:13,809 --> 00:07:14,802
滾！
Beat it!

60
00:07:18,801 --> 00:07:20,239
鄙惡之人！
Foul thing!

61
00:07:21,012 --> 00:07:23,856
願神降罪於你！你是殺人凶手！
A pox on your throat!
Thou art a murderer!

62
00:07:24,295 --> 00:07:25,699
殺人凶手！
A bloody murderer!

63
00:07:30,962 --> 00:07:33,337
我要為我兄弟複仇！
My brother's death shall be avenged!

64
00:07:47,714 --> 00:07:49,849
團隊，候令！
Company, halt!

65
00:07:53,978 --> 00:07:55,542
除去他的項圈！
Get that yoke off him!

66
00:08:09,456 --> 00:08:12,334
你不是我的奴隸
You, sir, are not one of my vassals.

67
00:08:14,147 --> 00:08:15,551
你是誰？
Who are you?

68
00:08:16,491 --> 00:08:18,158
誰在問？
Who wants to know?

69
00:08:19,305 --> 00:08:22,549
我是紅衣亨利，薛爾公爵
I am Henry the Red. Duke of Shale.

70
00:08:22,924 --> 00:08:25,836
北陸之王，也是人民的領導者
Lord of the Northlands
and leader of its peoples.

71
00:08:26,777 --> 00:08:31,197
噢，哈囉，美褲先生
跟你說吧，老兄
Well, hello, Mister Fancy Pants.
I got news for you, pal.

72
00:08:31,400 --> 00:08:34,472
現在你只領導兩樣事情
狗跟屎
You ain't leading but two things right now,
jack and shit.

73
00:08:34,850 --> 00:08:37,522
-這堥S狗
-閉上鳥嘴！
. And Jack left town.
. Shut your bleedin' hole!

74
00:08:37,865 --> 00:08:40,674
紳士們，亞瑟王！
Gentlemen, Lord Arthur!

75
00:08:49,256 --> 00:08:51,928
惡魔已蘇醒了
There is an evil awakened in this land.

76
00:08:52,941 --> 00:08:56,652
我的手下拼命抵抗...
And while my people fight
for their very souls against it...

77
00:08:56,861 --> 00:08:59,602
...你，紅衣亨利，向我們宣戰
...you, Henry the Red, wage war on us.

78
00:08:59,910 --> 00:09:01,382
騙子！
Charlatan!

79
00:09:03,729 --> 00:09:06,710
是你先攻擊我們的
It was you who first turned
your swords on us.

80
00:09:06,778 --> 00:09:09,782
這個惡魔也已敗壞了我的手下！
And this evil has befouled
my people as well!

81
00:09:09,861 --> 00:09:13,001
你的手下也不見得比那深坑堛...
Your people are no better
than the foul corruption...

82
00:09:13,076 --> 00:09:15,279
惡魔好多少...
...that lies in the bowels of that pit!

83
00:09:15,455 --> 00:09:17,327
對！你也好不了多少！
Right! You're no better!

84
00:09:17,532 --> 00:09:20,033
願神憐憫你的靈魂
May God have mercy upon your souls.

85
00:09:35,120 --> 00:09:38,398
天啊！是什麼東西？
In God's name!
What hell. Spawned thing lurks there?

86
00:09:43,931 --> 00:09:47,540
把他丟進深坑去跟嗜血雜種作伴
Into the pit
with those bloodthirsty sons of whores.

87
00:09:48,119 --> 00:09:49,215
走！
Move!

88
00:09:49,895 --> 00:09:50,888
不！
No!

89
00:10:22,123 --> 00:10:24,761
天！天啊！
God! Heavenly God!

90
00:10:28,790 --> 00:10:30,286
他逃走了！
He's escaping!

91
00:10:31,705 --> 00:10:33,201
抓住他！
Hold him!

92
00:11:07,586 --> 00:11:10,087
他們看起來沒那麼精明了吧？
They don't look so clever now, do they?

93
00:11:10,165 --> 00:11:11,832
他嚇壞了！
He's frightened!

94
00:11:14,856 --> 00:11:18,236
喂，喂！等等
Whoa, whoa! Wait a minute.

95
00:11:19,647 --> 00:11:21,816
等等，等一下！
Hold it. Wait a minute!

96
00:11:21,992 --> 00:11:24,059
你得了解，老兄
You gotta understand, man.

97
00:11:24,705 --> 00:11:27,617
我之前從沒見過這些混球！
I never even saw these assholes before!

98
00:11:28,558 --> 00:11:29,928
他嚇壞了！
He trembles!

99
00:11:31,842 --> 00:11:33,578
你在等什麼？
What are you waiting for?

100
00:11:33,985 --> 00:11:36,360
亨利，你得告訴他們，你不認識我
Henry, you gotta tell them
you don't know me.

101
00:11:37,068 --> 00:11:38,975
我們素未謀面，說啊！
We never met, tell them!

102
00:11:41,691 --> 00:11:44,100
他不會聽的，小兄弟
I do not think he'll listen, lad.

103
00:11:46,013 --> 00:11:50,228
聽清楚，你們抓錯人了
Look, I'm telling you.
You've got the wrong guy.

104
00:12:00,753 --> 00:12:03,791
跟你說你們抓錯人了
I'm telling you, you got the wrong guy.

105
00:13:20,253 --> 00:13:21,520
啊，你...
Why, you...

106
00:13:26,787 --> 00:13:31,435
-鐵釘
-他說鐵釘！上鐵釘！
. Spikes.
. Hey, he said spikes! Give him spikes!

107
00:13:45,715 --> 00:13:48,490
讓開！陌生人！
Make way! Strange one!

108
00:14:00,456 --> 00:14:01,484
陌生人！
Strange one!

109
00:14:26,788 --> 00:14:29,197
詛咒你
Damn you.

110
00:15:54,295 --> 00:15:56,738
你的鞋帶松了
You know, your shoelace is untied.

111
00:16:07,697 --> 00:16:09,033
好
All right.

112
00:16:10,812 --> 00:16:12,342
誰來挑戰？
Who wants some?

113
00:16:13,324 --> 00:16:14,957
該誰來？
Who's next?

114
00:16:17,244 --> 00:16:18,716
來啊？
How about it?

115
00:16:19,321 --> 00:16:23,741
誰來？誰要來挑戰？
Who wants some?
Who wants to have a little?

116
00:16:28,535 --> 00:16:29,528
你
You.

117
00:16:33,593 --> 00:16:35,260
你要打嗎？
You want some more?

118
00:16:39,858 --> 00:16:41,330
要嗎？
You want a little?

119
00:16:44,012 --> 00:16:46,650
你？要不要打？
Do you? You want some more?

120
00:17:03,745 --> 00:17:06,315
快滾
Now, get on those horses
and get out of here.

121
00:17:09,943 --> 00:17:11,347
放他們走！
Let them go!

122
00:17:34,868 --> 00:17:35,861
停！
Halt!

123
00:17:37,347 --> 00:17:39,620
謝謝你們的款待！
Thank you, generous hosts!

124
00:17:41,167 --> 00:17:42,765
拿劍的人！
Sword boy!

125
00:17:50,647 --> 00:17:54,358
驕傲的人，我要將你殺死
For that arrogance, I shall see you dead.

126
00:18:00,933 --> 00:18:02,165
巫術！
Sorcery!

127
00:18:04,920 --> 00:18:06,016
好
Yeah.

128
00:18:07,063 --> 00:18:10,135
你們這些未開化的白癡們，聽好了
All right, you primitive screwheads,
listen up.

129
00:18:11,151 --> 00:18:12,555
看到這個？
See this?

130
00:18:13,563 --> 00:18:17,240
這是我的槍
This is my boom stick!

131
00:18:18,588 --> 00:18:22,837
12厘米，雙排雷敏頓槍
美而廉超市的頂尖貨色
It's a 12.gauge, double. Barreled Remington.
S. Mart's top of the line.

132
00:18:23,613 --> 00:18:26,148
可以在運動器材部門購買
You can find this
in the sporting goods department.

133
00:18:26,729 --> 00:18:29,973
沒錯，這把槍是在密西根州出品
That's right, this sweet baby was made
in Grand Rapids, Michigan.

134
00:18:30,381 --> 00:18:32,824
零售價是109.95美元
It retails for about $109.95.

135
00:18:33,330 --> 00:18:38,048
槍托是由核桃木做成
槍身由精鐵打造，配上靈敏板機
It's got a walnut stock,
cobalt. Blue steel, and a hair trigger.

136
00:18:38,723 --> 00:18:43,543
對啦，絕對物超所值
That's right. Shop smart. Shop S. Mart.

137
00:18:44,284 --> 00:18:45,882
懂了嗎？
You got that?

138
00:18:46,897 --> 00:18:48,667
我發誓...
Now, I swear...

139
00:18:49,611 --> 00:18:51,986
...你們誰要是敢...
...the next one of you primates...

140
00:18:52,660 --> 00:18:54,829
...再碰我一下...
...even touches me...

141
00:19:24,386 --> 00:19:28,932
來談談我該怎麼回去吧
Now, let's talk about how I get back home.

142
00:20:00,233 --> 00:20:02,642
我懇求您的寬恕，陛下
I prithee to forgive me, my Lord.

143
00:20:03,047 --> 00:20:05,548
我以為您是亨利的同黨
I believed thee one of Henry's men.

144
00:20:05,895 --> 00:20:08,967
一開始你要殺我，現在你要吻我
First you wanna kill me,
now you wanna kiss me.

145
00:20:10,652 --> 00:20:11,714
滾
Blow.

146
00:20:15,979 --> 00:20:18,823
怎麼樣？能不能送我回去？
So what's the deal?
Can you send me back or not?

147
00:20:18,894 --> 00:20:23,406
只有死亡志記才有能力
我們也在找這本邪惡的書
Only the Necronomicon has the power,
an unholy book which we also require.

148
00:20:23,684 --> 00:20:27,567
書中記載著如何讓你回到自己的時空
Within its pages are passages
that can send you back to your time.

149
00:20:27,772 --> 00:20:30,444
只有你，上天的使者，才能拿到它
Only you, the promised one,
can quest for it.

150
00:20:31,725 --> 00:20:34,763
我不要你的書，也不聽你廢話
I don't want your book.
I don't want your bullshit!

151
00:20:34,840 --> 00:20:38,220
趕快把我送回我的時空
快！快！快...
Just send me back to my own time.
Pronto! Today! Chop...

152
00:20:48,509 --> 00:20:51,387
你該死
You shall die!

153
00:20:56,885 --> 00:21:00,129
你絕不可以拿死亡志記
You shall never take the Necronomicon.

154
00:21:00,838 --> 00:21:04,687
我們將飽餐你的靈魂
We shall feast upon your souls!

155
00:21:28,108 --> 00:21:30,449
那是魔法，拿斧頭來
It's a trick. Get an ax.

156
00:21:37,992 --> 00:21:39,899
守衛！殺死他！
Guards! Kill her!

157
00:21:41,342 --> 00:21:43,683
抓住巫婆！抓住她！
Capture the witch! Capture the witch!

158
00:21:44,457 --> 00:21:47,529
我的眼睛！我瞎了！天，我瞎了！
My eyes! I'm blind! Oh, God, I'm blind!

159
00:21:49,617 --> 00:21:50,610
不！
No!

160
00:21:56,149 --> 00:21:57,621
喂，妖女！
Yo, she. Bitch!

161
00:21:59,400 --> 00:22:00,667
來啊
Let's go.

162
00:22:23,353 --> 00:22:26,162
如果死亡志記落在邪惡人手中...
If the Necronomicon fell into
the hands of the Deadites...

163
00:22:26,268 --> 00:22:28,838
...所有人類都會被惡魔消滅
...all mankind will be consumed
by this evil.

164
00:22:28,948 --> 00:22:31,357
現在你願意去取書了嗎？
Now will thou quest for the book?

165
00:22:45,264 --> 00:22:46,531
那個
That one.

166
00:23:13,774 --> 00:23:15,178
太棒了
Groovy.

167
00:23:28,715 --> 00:23:31,753
怎麼？你在農場長大的啊？
關上門
What's the matter, you raised in a barn?
Shut the door.

168
00:23:32,133 --> 00:23:35,273
大概是跟這些原始人一樣
都在農場長大的
Probably was raised in a barn,
with all the other primitives.

169
00:23:44,462 --> 00:23:47,534
智者說你是上天派遣來的
The Wisemen say that thou art
the promised one.

170
00:23:51,397 --> 00:23:54,309
據說你要去取書來幫助我們
'Tis said thou wilt journey for the book
to help us.

