Coward.

342
00:54:15,708 --> 00:54:18,689
-救我！
-席拉！
. Help me!
. Sheila!

343
00:54:32,492 --> 00:54:34,970
別放箭！你會傷了她
Hold your arms! You'll hit the girl.

344
00:54:40,098 --> 00:54:41,365
拿劍來
My sword.

345
00:54:46,463 --> 00:54:47,730
可惡！
Damn you!

346
00:55:06,564 --> 00:55:08,036
挖，用力挖！
Dig, damn you!

347
00:55:09,345 --> 00:55:11,183
挖快點！
Dig faster!

348
00:55:11,455 --> 00:55:15,201
我將統領所有在戰斗中死去
滿身爬滿螻蟻的鬼東西
I shall command every worm. Infested
son of a bitch that ever died in battle.

349
00:55:15,275 --> 00:55:16,839
-謝謝您
-你！
. Thank you, sir.
. You there!

350
00:55:16,916 --> 00:55:18,549
很好！
Handsomely, now!

351
00:55:18,659 --> 00:55:21,468
我們去攻擊他們的城堡
拿回我的書
We shall storm their castle
and get my book.

352
00:55:21,874 --> 00:55:23,873
起來，你們這些惡棍
Hoist, you damnable varlets!

353
00:55:28,775 --> 00:55:32,019
歡迎回到活人的地盤
Welcome back to the land of the living.

354
00:55:32,729 --> 00:55:35,333
拿起鏟子來快挖！
Now pick up a shovel and get digging!

355
00:55:37,520 --> 00:55:39,221
把女人帶來！
Bring on the wench!

356
00:55:39,831 --> 00:55:41,361
下去！
Get down there!

357
00:55:51,255 --> 00:55:53,162
給我一個吻，寶貝
Give me some sugar, baby.

358
00:55:59,363 --> 00:56:03,144
你真是可愛啊？
Now ain't you the sweet little thing?

359
00:56:06,499 --> 00:56:09,377
別碰我，你這惡心的東西！
Don't touch me, you foul thing!

360
00:56:15,886 --> 00:56:19,095
來，乖
Come on. That's it.

361
00:56:33,072 --> 00:56:35,813
你要派上用場囉，快走！
We got plans for you, girly. Girl! Move!

362
00:56:37,628 --> 00:56:41,100
快拼命挖，快點！
Bust your bones, you dig up holes, dogs!
Get thee hence!

363
00:56:51,063 --> 00:56:52,799
有探子來報！
A scout approaches!

364
00:57:00,074 --> 00:57:01,570
牽著馬
Get his horse!

365
00:57:02,520 --> 00:57:03,650
起來
Arise.

366
00:57:03,726 --> 00:57:07,541
陛下，死亡軍團在野地上聚集
正朝著城堡過來
My Lord, an army of the dead gather
in the wilderness and approach the castle.

367
00:57:07,612 --> 00:57:10,055
-多遠？
-才兩天的路程
. How far from here?
. But two days ride.

368
00:57:10,192 --> 00:57:13,938
-有翅膀的是前鋒
-也許我們該快逃
. These winged ones are only the first.
. Perhaps we should leave soon.

369
00:57:14,011 --> 00:57:16,649
-到山中可保安全
-是，我們快逃！
. We'll be safe in the mountains.
. Yes. We must flee!

370
00:57:16,758 --> 00:57:19,796
-書上已記載了，這是注定的
-他們會奪走我們的靈魂
. It is written. It's been foretold.
. They'll take our souls.

371
00:57:19,908 --> 00:57:21,883
-我怕！
-所有人的靈魂！
. I'm afraid!
. Every one of our souls!

372
00:57:21,951 --> 00:57:23,618
我不想死
I don't want to die.

373
00:57:24,598 --> 00:57:28,573
好啊！快逃啊！
That's it! Go ahead and run!

374
00:57:29,623 --> 00:57:33,300
逃回家去跟媽媽哭啊！我？
Run home and cry to mama! Me?

375
00:57:34,782 --> 00:57:36,552
我不願再逃了！
I'm through running!

376
00:57:38,702 --> 00:57:41,237
我說我們留下來跟他們拼命
I say we stay here and fight it out.

377
00:57:41,784 --> 00:57:45,930
未來的人都跟你一樣會說大話嗎？
Are all men from the future
loudmouth braggarts?

378
00:57:46,341 --> 00:57:49,219
不，只有我才這樣
No. Just me, baby.

379
00:57:49,925 --> 00:57:50,895
只有我
Just me.

380
00:57:52,036 --> 00:57:55,508
我們如何在城堡牆邊抵抗死亡軍團？
How will we fight an army of the dead
at our castle walls?

381
00:57:55,888 --> 00:58:00,742
怎麼跟他們拼命？用說的嗎？
大部分的人都逃走了
How will you fight that? More words?
Most of our people have already fled.

382
00:58:00,981 --> 00:58:02,922
這堨u剩60個人
We are but 60 men.

383
00:58:04,131 --> 00:58:07,774
我們可以找紅衣亨利的人來幫忙
Then we'll get Henry the Red
and his men to fight with us.

384
00:58:10,395 --> 00:58:14,438
誰願意加入？
Now! Who's with me?

385
00:58:28,721 --> 00:58:30,525
我跟隨你
I'll stand by you.

386
00:58:32,774 --> 00:58:36,989
-我願意效力
-我會獻出勇氣！
. You can count on my steel.
. I'll offer up my courage!

387
00:58:37,331 --> 00:58:40,540
-我與你共進退！
-我站在你這邊！
. Me sword's by your side!
. I'm with you!

388
00:58:41,116 --> 00:58:43,149
我為你效力
I'll bend my bow to your will, sir.

389
00:58:47,549 --> 00:58:50,724
萬歲！萬歲！萬歲！
Hail! Hail! Hail!

390
00:59:07,616 --> 00:59:11,625
親愛的，跟大夥打個招呼
Well, my dear, say hello to the boys.

391
00:59:18,203 --> 00:59:20,681
很久沒見這麼美的人了
There's a sight for sore bones.

392
00:59:25,138 --> 00:59:29,856
我壞到骨頭堣F
I may be bad, but I feel good.

393
00:59:31,771 --> 00:59:34,409
-誰是統領？
-您，陛下
. Who rules?
. It is you, my lord.

394
00:59:34,519 --> 00:59:36,015
向城堡前進！
To the castle!

395
00:59:38,807 --> 00:59:40,645
-但大家都怕！
-太重了！夠了
. But the men are afraid!
. It's too heavy! Now, that's enough.

396
00:59:40,717 --> 00:59:42,886
別抱怨了！
Quit your bellyaching!

397
00:59:43,966 --> 00:59:48,146
我知道你們怕，我們都怕
I know you're scared. We're all scared.

398
00:59:49,662 --> 00:59:52,163
但這不表示我們怯懦
But that doesn't mean we're cowards.

399
00:59:52,844 --> 00:59:55,756
我們能打敗他們，一定能！
We can take these Deadites,
we can take them!

400
00:59:57,434 --> 00:59:58,838
運用科學
With science.

401
01:00:03,029 --> 01:00:04,901
快，快！
Hurry up, now!

402
01:00:05,608 --> 01:00:08,051
快！推，一起來！
Come on, fellas! Push! Heave ho!

403
01:00:21,857 --> 01:00:24,026
基礎化學

404
01:00:27,586 --> 01:00:29,390
蒸氣廠運作

405
01:01:00,217 --> 01:01:01,587
傾斜，傾斜
Tilt. Tilt.

406
01:01:02,964 --> 01:01:04,402
好，來，來
Okay, in, in.

407
01:01:13,617 --> 01:01:15,021
火藥

408
01:01:50,402 --> 01:01:53,943
來了！死亡軍團來了！
They're coming! The Deadites approach!

409
01:01:59,581 --> 01:02:03,030
快，你這些沒用的人！
他們就要到了！
Quickly now, you worthless fools!
They'll be on us anon!

410
01:02:03,167 --> 01:02:04,639
快！
Come on, guys!

411
01:02:08,929 --> 01:02:13,075
就要見真章了
你們最好別讓我失望
The moment of truth is almost here.
You men better not fail me now.

412
01:02:29,566 --> 01:02:31,769
他們聲勢如此浩大
There's so damned many of them.

413
01:02:45,279 --> 01:02:46,877
我需要多一點人手
I need more men.

414
01:03:30,036 --> 01:03:34,011
戰壘！堆起石頭！快！
Battle stations! Get those rocks up!
On the double!

415
01:03:34,392 --> 01:03:38,504
准備好彈弓！
讓他們知道我們的厲害！
Ready the catapults!
By God, let's give them what for!

416
01:03:48,229 --> 01:03:49,325
停！
Halt!

417
01:04:54,260 --> 01:04:56,932
-望遠鏡！
-遵命
. Looking glass!
. Aye, sire.

418
01:05:04,780 --> 01:05:07,223
拿到死亡志記後...
Once I possess the Necronomicon...

419
01:05:08,466 --> 01:05:13,480
...我會統治一切，你就是我的皇後
...I shall rule, and you shall be my queen.

420
01:05:27,964 --> 01:05:30,910
陛下，我們已經兩面都布置好了
My lord, we are positioned on both fronts.

421
01:05:30,979 --> 01:05:34,359
好，他們把我的書放哪堙H
Fine. Where are they keeping my book?

422
01:05:34,731 --> 01:05:37,609
那堙A陛下
在第二層牆的吊橋後面
There, my lord.
Beyond the drawbridge in the second wall.

423
01:05:37,679 --> 01:05:39,712
那是最安全的地方
That would be the safest place.

424
01:05:39,790 --> 01:05:44,508
沒有人能阻撓我取得死亡志記
I will not allow anything to keep me
from possessing that Necronomicon.

425
01:05:46,323 --> 01:05:50,572
現在，向城堡邁進
Now, bring me forth into that castle.

426
01:05:50,946 --> 01:05:54,155
-前進！
-前進！
. Forward!
. Forward!

427
01:05:54,296 --> 01:05:58,111
大肆破壞，放出戰狗！
Cry havoc, and let loose the dogs of war!

428
01:05:58,719 --> 01:06:01,631
攻向城堡！
To the castle!

429
01:06:05,720 --> 01:06:06,987
很好
Excellent.

430
01:06:10,042 --> 01:06:12,485
殺光活人！
Death to the mortals!

431
01:06:15,704 --> 01:06:16,902
箭！
Arrows!

432
01:06:17,479 --> 01:06:18,575
弓
Bows.

433
01:06:19,322 --> 01:06:20,418
上弦！
Load!

434
01:06:22,204 --> 01:06:23,266
滿弓！
Draw!

435
01:06:33,862 --> 01:06:35,529
火把！
Torch boy!

436
01:07:17,951 --> 01:07:19,149
穩住
Steady.

437
01:07:26,159 --> 01:07:27,255
發射！
Fire!

438
01:07:29,978 --> 01:07:32,684
前進，邪魔！前進！
Advance, you demons! Advance!

439
01:07:53,998 --> 01:07:56,910
對啦，寶貝！
Yeah, baby!

440
01:08:04,183 --> 01:08:05,519
好！
All right!

441
01:08:06,695 --> 01:08:09,401
-撤退！
-快逃啊！
. Retreat!
. Let's get the hell out of here!

442
01:08:19,695 --> 01:08:20,962
他真可惡！
Damn him!

443
01:08:21,839 --> 01:08:24,614
側面的第二突擊隊會成功的
The sortie on the second flank will stand.

444
01:08:24,786 --> 01:08:26,316
一定得成功！
It must!

445
01:08:27,701 --> 01:08:31,412
長官，南面有第二波的攻擊
Sire, there's a second division
approaching from the south.

446
01:08:32,057 --> 01:08:34,729
沖進城門！
Ram the gates!

447
01:08:39,125 --> 01:08:40,461
彈弓手！
Catapults!

448
01:08:40,902 --> 01:08:43,037
彈弓手！南面！
Catapults! South!

449
01:08:49,980 --> 01:08:53,863
-我們會擊敗他們！
-再度攻擊！
. We'll crush them!
. We'll strike again!

450
01:09:06,296 --> 01:09:07,792
發射！
Fire!

451
01:09:15,442 --> 01:09:16,744
哪來的火？
What the blazes?

452
01:09:24,889 --> 01:09:26,888
-小心！
-讓開！
. Watch out!
. Make way!

453
01:09:33,801 --> 01:09:35,171
快躲起來！
Seek cover!

454
01:09:44,789 --> 01:09:47,598
你們這些爛骨頭！
You miserable bags of bones!

455
01:09:47,772 --> 01:09:51,381
快爬起來再...
Pick yourselves up and sally for...

456
01:09:52,562 --> 01:09:53,898
再...
Sally for...

457
01:09:55,141 --> 01:09:57,140
再沖
Sally forth.

458
01:10:00,938 --> 01:10:03,245
快，你們這些沒用的東西！
Come on, you miserable wretches!

459
01:10:13,936 --> 01:10:15,032
前進！
Forward!

460
01:10:17,789 --> 01:10:20,290
鞏固城門！快！
Buttress that door! Now!

461
01:10:37,321 --> 01:10:38,485
石塊！
Rocks!

462
01:10:39,732 --> 01:10:40,896
可惡！
Damn you!

463
01:10:44,657 --> 01:10:46,758
一定很痛！
That's gotta hurt!

464
01:10:47,170 --> 01:10:48,540
混帳東西！
You cretins!

465
01:10:48,878 --> 01:10:50,076
箭！
Arrows!

466
01:10:51,291 --> 01:10:52,284
發射！
Fire!

467
01:10:57,757 --> 01:11:00,429
我們要讓那混帳好看！
We'll ram it down the bastard's throat!

468
01:11:01,878 --> 01:11:02,940
發射！
Fire!

469
01:11:08,444 --> 01:11:11,082
南面側攻隊，到西牆去！快！
South flank, to the western wall! Now!

470
01:11:11,660 --> 01:11:15,303
紅衣亨利呢？早告訴你他不會來！
Where is Henry the Red?
I told you he would not come!

471
01:11:15,378 --> 01:11:20,198
戴好你的罐頭帽子，鐵頭！
我說他會來，他就是會來！
Keep your sardine can on, bucket. Head!
I said he'll be here, he'll be here!

472
01:11:20,605 --> 01:11:23,311
我不認為，但我要告訴你
I think he will not. But know this.

473
01:11:23,721 --> 01:11:28,575
無論戰役結果如何
認為你是懦夫是我的錯
No matter how this battle fares,
I was wrong to think you a coward.

474
01:11:34,374 --> 01:11:37,183
沖破了！城陷了！
We've broken through! The castle is ours!

475
01:11:42,180 --> 01:11:44,852
殺光活人！
Kill the mortals!

476
01:11:49,617 --> 01:11:51,147
好了！
All right, men!

477
01:12:21,344 --> 01:12:24,690
他們沖破了第一道牆！
接下來怎麼辦？
They've breached the first wall!
What next?

478
01:12:31,696 --> 01:12:34,139
我們被遺棄了！
We are deserted!

479
01:12:35,180 --> 01:12:37,715
向後退！守衛城牆！
Fall back! Man the parapet!

480
01:12:38,128 --> 01:12:39,726
保護死亡志記！
Protect the book!

481
01:12:41,076 --> 01:12:42,640
願神救助
God save us all.

482
01:12:43,556 --> 01:12:47,439
爬上樓梯，小子！
到安全的牆後去！
Up the ladders, lads!
To the safety of the parapets!

483
01:12:57,460 --> 01:12:59,767
與21世紀打個招呼
Say hello to the 21st century.

484
01:13:12,938 --> 01:13:15,508
來！人人有份！
Come on! I got plenty for everybody!

485
01:13:24,497 --> 01:13:27,101
-滋味不錯吧？
-裝死！
. How do you like this?
. Play dead!

486
01:13:29,856 --> 01:13:32,265
抓住車上的人！
It's the one in the cart we want. Get him!

487
01:13:50,460 --> 01:13:52,493
再見啦，蠢蛋！
<i>Sayonara</i>, sucker!

488
01:13:59,137 --> 01:14:00,301
你...
Why, you...

489
01:14:02,320 --> 01:14:04,798
你逃不出我的手掌心！
You can run, but you can't hide!

490
01:14:31,199 --> 01:14:32,397
席拉？
Sheila?

491
01:14:57,799 --> 01:15:00,300
-我們已拿下庭院了，陛下
-很好
. We've secured the courtyard, my lord.
. Excellent.

492
01:15:01,183 --> 01:15:03,958
該是拿書的時候了，把牆撞破！
Now I will have that book.
Storm the walls!

493
01:15:04,432 --> 01:15:05,528
樓梯！
Ladders!

494
01:15:05,605 --> 01:15:09,488
來，你們這些死人骨頭！快！
不然我送你們進沾膠廠！
Come on, you bony devils! Hurry up!
Or I'll send you to the glue factory!

495
01:15:09,558 --> 01:15:10,722
強力膠！
Elmer!

496
01:15:11,535 --> 01:15:13,007
往牆進攻！
To the walls!

497
01:15:16,292 --> 01:15:18,896
我把你切成一片片的！不，不！
I'll slice you to ribbons! No, no!

498
01:15:43,730 --> 01:15:45,466
慢著！小心！
Wait! Look out!

499
01:15:53,010 --> 01:15:56,185
-嘿，你是我的人，甜心！
-走開！
. Hey, you're mine, sweetie!
. Get off of her!

500
01:16:03,396 --> 01:16:04,663
可惡！
Damn you!

501
01:16:05,372 --> 01:16:09,952
守護死亡志記，小子們！
否則就死在惡魔的火
Defend the Necronomicon, lads!
Or perish in the devil's fire!

502
01:16:14,653 --> 01:16:17,359
-陛下
-看好志記！
. My lord.
. Stay with the book!

503
01:16:17,567 --> 01:16:19,439
志記會是我們的！
The book will be ours!

504
01:16:41,990 --> 01:16:43,018
嗨！
Hello!

505
01:16:53,582 --> 01:16:55,215
這書是我的！
The book is mine!

506
01:16:59,813 --> 01:17:01,285
拿去！
There you go!

507
01:17:09,663 --> 01:17:11,662
我把你剁個稀巴爛
I'll cut your gizzard out.

508
01:17:12,678 --> 01:17:14,150
去哪了？
Where'd he go?

509
01:17:25,342 --> 01:17:26,814
來吧！
Come to Papa!

510
01:17:28,089 --> 01:17:29,321
去抓他！
Get him!

511
01:17:59,547 --> 01:18:03,933
瘋女人，走開！
你要把我眼睛挖出來了！
Crazy bitch, get off me!
You're tearing my eyes out!

512
01:18:05,209 --> 01:18:06,545
妖女！
You witch!

513
01:18:13,450 --> 01:18:14,420
對
Right.

514
01:18:22,027 --> 01:18:24,162
你以前認為我很美的
You found me beautiful once.

515
01:18:24,841 --> 01:18:27,376
蜜糖，你變成醜八怪了
Honey, you got real ugly.

516
01:18:46,818 --> 01:18:48,382
在這
There we are.

517
01:18:57,337 --> 01:18:59,175
你要來狠的？
You wanna play rough?

518
01:19:10,571 --> 01:19:11,803
好！
All right!

519
01:19:35,296 --> 01:19:36,963
你慘了！
You're going down!

520
01:19:38,076 --> 01:19:40,577
-我往上走！
-我追你到底！
. I'm going up!
. I'm coming for you!

521
01:20:12,114 --> 01:20:13,244
抓他！
Get him!

